{"type":"text","timestamp":1777014446007,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"id":"prt_dbe4ed1b9002VrP0h7WbGkZ2Ln","messageID":"msg_dbe4ea830001IVzSvtnIhuDT8w","sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","type":"text","text":"千束，我建议 `project-manager` 的结构要分成两层：\n\n1. **项目内结构**：每个项目自己的 `.agent-project/`，负责长期事实来源。\n2. **全局注册/索引结构**：project-manager 自己维护一个 registry/index，负责跨项目查询。\n\n也就是说，不要只靠扫描每个项目的 README；也不要只靠全局 registry。  \n应该是：\n\n```text\n项目内 .agent-project/ = 单项目真相来源\n全局 registry/index   = 查询加速与统一入口\n```\n\n这样才能支持你说的：\n\n- 按状态查\n- 按名称查\n- 按生命周期查\n- 按项目类型查\n- 按持续/有限项目查\n- 按当前阶段查\n- 按健康度查\n- 按是否需要用户处理查\n- 按更新时间/陈旧状态查\n- 按标签/领域/owner 查\n\n---\n\n# 1. 设计参考\n\n我刚查了本地和外部模式，几个结论很明确。\n\n## 1.1 本地已有旧模式：`project-skill-manager`\n\n旧的 `project-skill-manager` 是通过扫描：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\*/README.md\n```\n\n读取 README YAML frontmatter：\n\n```yaml\n---\nname: 项目名称\ndescription: 一句话描述项目\nstatus: todo/done/sustained\n---\n```\n\n脚本返回：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"项目名称\",\n  \"status\": \"状态\",\n  \"description\": \"描述\",\n  \"path\": \"项目路径\"\n}\n```\n\n这个模式的优点：\n\n- 简单\n- 人类可编辑\n- 可以按 status 过滤\n- 适合早期\n\n缺点也明显：\n\n- status 太粗\n- 查询字段太少\n- 无生命周期、阶段、健康度、持续运行信息\n- README 既做人类文档又做机器事实来源，容易混乱\n- 不适合复杂查询和持续项目\n\n所以新设计应该继承它的“可扫描、可注册、可查询”思想，但升级为结构化 `.agent-project/project.json`。\n\n---\n\n## 1.2 本地 `skill-library` registry 模式\n\n`mycli skill-library` 当前有：\n\n```text\ncapability-library/mycli/skill-library/registry.json\n```\n\n它通过扫描 `SKILL.md` frontmatter 生成 registry，registry 用于快速查询。\n\n这个模式对 project-manager 很有价值：\n\n```text\nsource of truth: 每个 skill 的 SKILL.md\nquery index: mycli/skill-library/registry.json\n```\n\n迁移到项目管理就是：\n\n```text\nsource of truth: 每个项目的 .agent-project/project.json\nquery index: project-manager/registry.json 或 index.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## 1.3 agent-workflow 的项目结构\n\n`agent-workflow` 已经有一个很成熟的工程结构：\n\n```text\nmy-workflow/\n  workflow.json\n  README.md\n  .generated/\n    manifest.json\n    graph.json\n    scaffold.lock.json\n  context/\n  steps/\n  shared/\n  runtime/\n  var/\n```\n\n这说明我们在 project-manager 里也应该区分：\n\n```text\n人工维护的事实来源\n自动生成的索引/视图\n运行期产物\n```\n\n所以 `.agent-project/` 里也建议有：\n\n```text\n.generated/\nvar/\n```\n\n但第一版可以简化。\n\n---\n\n## 1.4 外部模式：Backstage / Kubernetes / Nx\n\n几个外部系统对查询很有启发。\n\n### Backstage\n\nBackstage 的 `catalog-info.yaml` 结构是：\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: backstage.io/v1alpha1\nkind: Component\nmetadata:\n  name: artist-web\n  description: ...\n  labels:\n    example.com/custom: value\n  annotations:\n    example.com/service-discovery: artistweb\n  tags:\n    - java\nspec:\n  type: website\n  lifecycle: production\n  owner: team\n  system: public-websites\n```\n\n核心启发：\n\n```text\nmetadata = 名称、描述、标签、链接、注解\nspec     = 类型、生命周期、owner、system\n```\n\n非常适合我们借鉴。\n\n### Kubernetes\n\nKubernetes 最强的是 labels/selectors：\n\n```yaml\nlabels:\n  app.kubernetes.io/name: wordpress\n  app.kubernetes.io/instance: wordpress-abcxyz\n  app.kubernetes.io/component: server\n  app.kubernetes.io/part-of: wordpress\n  app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: Helm\n```\n\n核心启发：\n\n- label 用于查询和分组\n- annotation 用于外部系统/说明性元数据\n- selector 支持多个条件 AND 查询\n\n### Nx\n\nNx `project.json` 支持：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"mylib\",\n  \"root\": \"libs/mylib\",\n  \"projectType\": \"library\",\n  \"tags\": [\"scope:myteam\"],\n  \"metadata\": {},\n  \"targets\": {}\n}\n```\n\n核心启发：\n\n- 每个项目有 `root`\n- 项目有 `projectType`\n- tags 用于图和查询\n- target 表示可执行动作\n\n对我们来说，`targets` 可以演化成“项目可执行动作/常用命令”，但 MVP 先不必重。\n\n---\n\n# 2. 总体结构\n\n我建议 project-manager 的数据结构分三层：\n\n```text\nProject Record       单项目事实来源\nProject Registry     已注册项目清单\nProject Index        查询优化索引/派生视图\n```\n\n对应文件：\n\n```text\n每个项目/\n  .agent-project/\n    project.json        # 单项目事实来源\n    status.md           # 人类可读当前状态\n    tasks/\n    next-actions/\n    decisions/\n    context/\n    operations/\n    artifacts/\n    runs/\n    handoffs/\n    reviews/\n    .generated/\n\nproject-manager自身/\n  registry.json         # 全局注册表\n  index.json            # 查询索引\n```\n\n---\n\n# 3. 单项目目录结构\n\n建议每个被管理项目内放：\n\n```text\n{project-root}/\n  .agent-project/\n    project.json\n    status.md\n\n    tasks/\n      task-0001.json\n      task-0002.json\n\n    next-actions/\n      next-0001.json\n      next-0002.json\n\n    decisions/\n      ADR-0001-something.md\n      index.json\n\n    context/\n      index.json\n      pinned-files.md\n      glossary.md\n      architecture.md\n\n    operations/\n      runbook.md\n      schedule.json\n      last-run.json\n      history.jsonl\n\n    artifacts/\n      index.json\n\n    runs/\n      agent-runs.json\n      workflow-runs.json\n\n    handoffs/\n      2026-04-24.md\n\n    reviews/\n      review-0001.md\n\n    .generated/\n      summary.json\n      search-doc.json\n      last-indexed.json\n```\n\n## 3.1 MVP 版本\n\n第一版不要太重，MVP 可以是：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/\n  project.json\n  status.md\n  tasks/\n  next-actions.json\n  decisions/\n  context/\n    index.json\n  operations/\n    runbook.md\n  runs/\n  handoffs/\n  .generated/\n```\n\n---\n\n# 4. `project.json` 结构设计\n\n我建议采用类似 Backstage 的 envelope：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"apiVersion\": \"agent-project/v1\",\n  \"kind\": \"Project\",\n  \"metadata\": {},\n  \"spec\": {},\n  \"status\": {},\n  \"current\": {},\n  \"operations\": {},\n  \"relations\": {},\n  \"timestamps\": {}\n}\n```\n\n为什么这样分？\n\n| 字段 | 作用 |\n|---|---|\n| `apiVersion` | schema 版本，方便以后迁移 |\n| `kind` | 未来可能有 ProjectGroup / Program |\n| `metadata` | 用于发现、展示、查询 |\n| `spec` | 项目本质定义，不频繁变化 |\n| `status` | 当前状态，经常变化 |\n| `current` | 当前推进项 |\n| `operations` | 持续运行项目运行状态 |\n| `relations` | 和 workflow、skill、repo、项目之间的关系 |\n| `timestamps` | 创建、更新、索引时间 |\n\n---\n\n# 5. 推荐 `project.json` 示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"apiVersion\": \"agent-project/v1\",\n  \"kind\": \"Project\",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"id\": \"daily-hot-news\",\n    \"name\": \"每日新闻热点收集\",\n    \"aliases\": [\"热点收集\", \"daily-news\"],\n    \"description\": \"每天自动收集和整理热点新闻主题。\",\n    \"root\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\",\n    \"owner\": \"千束\",\n    \"domain\": \"content-ops\",\n    \"tags\": [\"daily\", \"news\", \"hot-topics\", \"automation\"],\n    \"labels\": {\n      \"agent.project/type\": \"research\",\n      \"agent.project/mode\": \"ongoing\",\n      \"agent.project/domain\": \"content-ops\",\n      \"agent.project/managed-by\": \"project-manager\"\n    },\n    \"annotations\": {\n      \"notes\": \"持续运行型内容运营项目\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"spec\": {\n    \"project_type\": \"research\",\n    \"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\",\n    \"visibility\": \"private\",\n    \"source\": {\n      \"kind\": \"local\",\n      \"path\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\"\n    },\n    \"goals\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"goal-0001\",\n        \"title\": \"持续收集每日热点并生成摘要\",\n        \"status\": \"active\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"scope\": {\n      \"in\": [\n        \"热点采集\",\n        \"摘要生成\",\n        \"每日归档\"\n      ],\n      \"out\": [\n        \"自动发布到外部平台\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"status\": {\n    \"registration\": \"indexed\",\n    \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n    \"phase\": \"operations\",\n    \"activity\": \"stable\",\n    \"health\": \"green\",\n    \"delivery\": \"published\",\n    \"attention\": [],\n    \"summary\": \"每日热点收集稳定运行。\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n    \"updated_by\": \"scheduler\"\n  },\n  \"current\": {\n    \"goal_id\": \"goal-0001\",\n    \"milestone_id\": null,\n    \"task_id\": null,\n    \"next_action_id\": \"next-ops-check\",\n    \"summary\": \"等待下一次定时运行。\"\n  },\n  \"operations\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"cadence\": \"daily\",\n    \"trigger\": \"schedule\",\n    \"schedule_expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n    \"last_run_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"last_run_status\": \"success\",\n    \"last_success_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"next_run_at\": \"2026-04-25T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"consecutive_failures\": 0,\n    \"run_count_7d\": 7,\n    \"success_count_7d\": 7,\n    \"output_summary\": \"Collected 32 hot topics and generated daily digest.\",\n    \"runbook\": \".agent-project/operations/runbook.md\"\n  },\n  \"relations\": {\n    \"depends_on_projects\": [],\n    \"related_projects\": [],\n    \"workflows\": [],\n    \"skills\": [],\n    \"repos\": [],\n    \"artifacts\": []\n  },\n  \"timestamps\": {\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n    \"last_activity_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n    \"last_indexed_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:11:00+08:00\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 6. 为什么要有 `metadata.labels`\n\n`tags` 是人类友好的：\n\n```json\n\"tags\": [\"daily\", \"news\", \"automation\"]\n```\n\n`labels` 是机器查询友好的：\n\n```json\n\"labels\": {\n  \"agent.project/type\": \"research\",\n  \"agent.project/mode\": \"ongoing\",\n  \"agent.project/domain\": \"content-ops\"\n}\n```\n\n这样未来可以支持类似 Kubernetes 的 selector：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --selector \"agent.project/mode=ongoing,agent.project/domain=content-ops\"\n```\n\n第一版可以不实现完整 selector，但结构先留好。\n\n---\n\n# 7. 全局 Registry 结构\n\n项目查询不能每次都全盘扫描所有 `.agent-project/project.json`。  \n所以需要全局 registry。\n\n建议放在：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registry.json\n```\n\n或注册到 mycli 后：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\project-manager\\registry.json\n```\n\n我建议：\n\n- 源规则能力目录有模板和脚本\n- mycli 包里有实际 registry\n\n结构：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"schema_version\": \"agent-project-registry/v1\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:11:00+08:00\",\n  \"source_roots\": [\n    \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\",\n    \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\"\n  ],\n  \"projects\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"daily-hot-news\",\n      \"name\": \"每日新闻热点收集\",\n      \"aliases\": [\"热点收集\", \"daily-news\"],\n      \"description\": \"每天自动收集和整理热点新闻主题。\",\n      \"root\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\",\n      \"project_file\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\\\\.agent-project\\\\project.json\",\n      \"status_file\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\\\\.agent-project\\\\status.md\",\n      \"project_type\": \"research\",\n      \"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n      \"owner\": \"千束\",\n      \"domain\": \"content-ops\",\n      \"tags\": [\"daily\", \"news\", \"hot-topics\", \"automation\"],\n      \"labels\": {\n        \"agent.project/type\": \"research\",\n        \"agent.project/mode\": \"ongoing\"\n      },\n      \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n      \"phase\": \"operations\",\n      \"activity\": \"stable\",\n      \"health\": \"green\",\n      \"delivery\": \"published\",\n      \"attention\": [],\n      \"current_task_id\": null,\n      \"current_next_action_id\": \"next-ops-check\",\n      \"summary\": \"每日热点收集稳定运行。\",\n      \"last_activity_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n      \"last_indexed_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:11:00+08:00\",\n      \"is_missing\": false,\n      \"is_stale\": false\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 7.1 Registry 是摘要，不是真相来源\n\n必须明确：\n\n```text\nproject.json 是 truth\nregistry.json 是 index/cache\n```\n\n所以 registry 可以随时重建。\n\n---\n\n# 8. 进一步的 Index 结构\n\nRegistry 是项目列表。  \n如果项目多了，可以再生成查询索引。\n\n```text\nindex/\n  by-id.json\n  by-name.json\n  by-type.json\n  by-mode.json\n  by-lifecycle.json\n  by-phase.json\n  by-activity.json\n  by-health.json\n  by-delivery.json\n  by-attention.json\n  by-owner.json\n  by-tag.json\n  stale.json\n```\n\n但 MVP 不需要真的拆这么多文件。  \n第一版一个 `registry.json` 就够，查询时在内存里过滤。\n\n等项目很多了再生成：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"by_lifecycle\": {\n    \"active\": [\"daily-hot-news\", \"project-manager\"],\n    \"paused\": []\n  },\n  \"by_phase\": {\n    \"operations\": [\"daily-hot-news\"],\n    \"construction\": [\"project-manager\"]\n  },\n  \"by_tag\": {\n    \"automation\": [\"daily-hot-news\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 9. 查询模式设计\n\n你提到“基于状态，基于名称，基于生命周期什么的查询”，我建议 query 命令支持两层。\n\n## 9.1 简单参数查询\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query\nmycli project-manager query --name news\nmycli project-manager query --id daily-hot-news\nmycli project-manager query --type research\nmycli project-manager query --mode ongoing\nmycli project-manager query --lifecycle active\nmycli project-manager query --phase operations\nmycli project-manager query --activity stable\nmycli project-manager query --health yellow\nmycli project-manager query --delivery published\nmycli project-manager query --attention needs_maintenance\nmycli project-manager query --owner 千束\nmycli project-manager query --tag automation\nmycli project-manager query --domain content-ops\nmycli project-manager query --stale\n```\n\n支持组合：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --mode ongoing --health yellow\nmycli project-manager query --type capability --lifecycle active\nmycli project-manager query --phase maintenance --attention needs_unblock\n```\n\n默认 AND 语义。\n\n---\n\n## 9.2 Selector 查询\n\n未来支持：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --selector \"agent.project/mode=ongoing,agent.project/domain=content-ops\"\n```\n\n或者：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --where \"status.lifecycle=active,status.health!=green\"\n```\n\n但第一版不建议上复杂表达式。\n\n---\n\n# 10. 查询输出格式\n\n默认 table：\n\n```text\nid              name              type      mode     lifecycle  phase       activity  health  delivery   updated\ndaily-hot-news  每日热点新闻收集  research  ongoing  active     operations  stable    green   published  2026-04-24\nproject-manager Project Manager   capability finite   planned    requirements waiting  green   concept    2026-04-24\n```\n\nJSON：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --json\n```\n\n输出 registry entries。\n\n详细查看：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager get daily-hot-news\n```\n\n返回完整 `project.json`。\n\n---\n\n# 11. 推荐的查询字段清单\n\n## 11.1 基础查询字段\n\n```text\nid\nname\naliases\ndescription\nroot\nowner\ndomain\ntags\nlabels\n```\n\n## 11.2 类型查询字段\n\n```text\nproject_type\nproject_mode\nvisibility\npriority\n```\n\n## 11.3 状态查询字段\n\n```text\nregistration\nlifecycle\nphase\nactivity\nhealth\ndelivery\nattention\n```\n\n## 11.4 当前推进查询字段\n\n```text\ncurrent_task_id\ncurrent_next_action_id\ncurrent_goal_id\n```\n\n## 11.5 运行查询字段\n\n```text\noperations.enabled\noperations.cadence\noperations.trigger\noperations.last_run_status\noperations.consecutive_failures\noperations.next_run_at\n```\n\n## 11.6 时间查询字段\n\n```text\ncreated_at\nupdated_at\nlast_activity_at\nlast_indexed_at\nis_stale\n```\n\n---\n\n# 12. `status.md` 结构\n\n`status.md` 是给人和 agent 快速看的，不是主事实来源。\n\n```md\n# Project Status: 每日新闻热点收集\n\n## Summary\n\n每日热点收集稳定运行。\n\n## Current State\n\n- Type: research\n- Mode: ongoing\n- Lifecycle: active\n- Phase: operations\n- Activity: stable\n- Health: green\n- Delivery: published\n- Attention: none\n\n## Current Focus\n\n等待下一次定时运行。\n\n## Operations\n\n- Cadence: daily\n- Last Run: 2026-04-24 08:00\n- Last Run Status: success\n- Next Run: 2026-04-25 08:00\n- Consecutive Failures: 0\n\n## Next Actions\n\n- next-ops-check: Monitor next scheduled run.\n\n## Risks / Blockers\n\nNone.\n\n## Recent Updates\n\n- 2026-04-24: Collected 32 hot topics and generated daily digest.\n```\n\n原则：\n\n```text\nproject.json = 机器读\nstatus.md    = 人类/agent 快速读\n```\n\n---\n\n# 13. 任务与推进项结构\n\n项目结构必须支持“推进项”。\n\n我建议：\n\n```text\ntasks/\n  task-0001.json\nnext-actions/\n  next-0001.json\n```\n\n如果第一版想简单：\n\n```text\ntasks.json\nnext-actions.json\n```\n\n但长期看，还是“一个任务一个文件”更好，类似 taskmd 和 ADR。\n\n## 13.1 task 示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"task-0001\",\n  \"title\": \"设计 project-manager 项目结构\",\n  \"type\": \"design\",\n  \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n  \"priority\": \"high\",\n  \"phase\": \"architecture\",\n  \"owner\": \"assistant\",\n  \"depends_on\": [],\n  \"acceptance_criteria\": [\n    \"支持项目注册\",\n    \"支持按状态查询\",\n    \"支持按生命周期查询\",\n    \"支持持续项目结构\"\n  ],\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n## 13.2 next-action 示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"next-0001\",\n  \"title\": \"确认项目结构 v0.1\",\n  \"type\": \"decide\",\n  \"status\": \"open\",\n  \"priority\": \"high\",\n  \"owner\": \"千束\",\n  \"blocks\": [\"task-0002\"],\n  \"reason\": \"项目结构决定 registry、query、schema 的基础。\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 14. 项目注册流程\n\n## 14.1 init\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager init <project-root> --id <id> --name <name> --type <type> --mode finite|ongoing\n```\n\n生成：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/\n  project.json\n  status.md\n  tasks/\n  next-actions/\n  decisions/\n  context/\n  operations/\n  runs/\n  handoffs/\n  .generated/\n```\n\n## 14.2 register\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager register <project-root>\n```\n\n逻辑：\n\n1. 检查 `.agent-project/project.json`\n2. 读取 metadata/spec/status\n3. 写入/更新全局 `registry.json`\n4. 生成摘要字段\n5. 标记 `last_indexed_at`\n\n## 14.3 scan\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager scan D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\n```\n\n扫描：\n\n```text\n**/.agent-project/project.json\n```\n\n可兼容旧模式：\n\n```text\nREADME.md YAML frontmatter\n```\n\n如果发现旧格式：\n\n```yaml\nstatus: sustained\n```\n\n映射为：\n\n```json\n\"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n\"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n\"phase\": \"operations\"\n```\n\n---\n\n# 15. 旧状态迁移映射\n\n旧 `project-skill-manager` 状态：\n\n```text\ntodo\ndone\nsustained\nskill_dependent\n```\n\n映射建议：\n\n## `todo`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project_mode\": \"finite\",\n  \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n  \"phase\": \"construction\",\n  \"activity\": \"in_progress\"\n}\n```\n\n如果只是刚创建，也可以：\n\n```json\n\"lifecycle\": \"planned\"\n```\n\n## `done`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project_mode\": \"finite\",\n  \"lifecycle\": \"completed\",\n  \"phase\": \"closure\",\n  \"activity\": \"stable\"\n}\n```\n\n## `sustained`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n  \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n  \"phase\": \"operations\",\n  \"activity\": \"stable\"\n}\n```\n\n## `skill_dependent`\n\n不要作为主状态，而作为 protection/label：\n\n```json\n\"labels\": {\n  \"agent.project/protection\": \"skill-dependent\"\n}\n```\n\n或：\n\n```json\n\"protection\": [\"skill_dependent\", \"do_not_delete\"]\n```\n\n---\n\n# 16. 项目关系结构\n\n为了支持后面查“哪些项目依赖某技能/哪个 workflow 属于哪个项目”，要有 relations。\n\n```json\n\"relations\": {\n  \"depends_on_projects\": [\n    \"asset-library\"\n  ],\n  \"related_projects\": [\n    \"news-publisher\"\n  ],\n  \"workflows\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"daily_news_flow\",\n      \"path\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\\\\workflow.json\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"skills\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"news-collector\",\n      \"path\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\skill-library\\\\news-collector\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"repos\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"git\",\n      \"path\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\projects\\\\daily-hot-news\",\n      \"remote\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"artifacts\": []\n}\n```\n\n这样可以支持：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --depends-on asset-library\nmycli project-manager query --skill news-collector\nmycli project-manager query --workflow daily_news_flow\n```\n\n---\n\n# 17. 查询系统的推荐实现逻辑\n\n## 17.1 查询优先读 registry\n\n```text\nquery -> registry.json -> filter -> output\n```\n\n## 17.2 get 读 project.json\n\n```text\nget <id> -> registry 找 project_file -> 读完整 project.json\n```\n\n## 17.3 refresh 重建 registry\n\n```text\nrefresh/scan -> 扫描 source_roots -> 重建 registry\n```\n\n## 17.4 stale 计算\n\n不要把 stale 完全写死，可以查询时计算：\n\n```text\nis_stale = now - status.updated_at > stale_after_days\n```\n\n项目也可以配置：\n\n```json\n\"spec\": {\n  \"stale_after_days\": 14\n}\n```\n\nongoing 项目可以更严格：\n\n```json\n\"operations\": {\n  \"stale_after_hours\": 36\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 18. 查询命令面建议\n\n```powershell\n# 列出全部\nmycli project-manager list\n\n# 查询\nmycli project-manager query --name project\nmycli project-manager query --type capability\nmycli project-manager query --mode ongoing\nmycli project-manager query --lifecycle active\nmycli project-manager query --phase operations\nmycli project-manager query --activity degraded\nmycli project-manager query --health red\nmycli project-manager query --delivery published\nmycli project-manager query --attention needs_maintenance\nmycli project-manager query --tag automation\nmycli project-manager query --owner 千束\nmycli project-manager query --domain content-ops\n\n# 组合查询\nmycli project-manager query --mode ongoing --health yellow\nmycli project-manager query --lifecycle active --attention needs_user_decision\n\n# 获取完整项目\nmycli project-manager get daily-hot-news\n\n# 状态摘要\nmycli project-manager status daily-hot-news\n\n# 重建索引\nmycli project-manager refresh\nmycli project-manager scan D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\n```\n\n---\n\n# 19. 我建议的最终目录落点\n\n## 19.1 project-manager 能力目录\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\\n  README.md\n  SKILL.md\n  USER_MANUAL.md\n  REGISTRATION.md\n\n  schemas/\n    project.schema.json\n    registry.schema.json\n    task.schema.json\n    next-action.schema.json\n    operation.schema.json\n\n  templates/\n    project.json\n    status.md\n    task.json\n    next-action.json\n    decision.md\n    runbook.md\n\n  scripts/\n    project-manager.ps1\n    register-to-mycli.ps1\n\n  src/\n    project_manager.py\n\n  examples/\n    finite_capability_project/\n    ongoing_asset_library/\n    ongoing_daily_news/\n\n  tests/\n```\n\n## 19.2 每个项目目录\n\n```text\n{project-root}/\n  .agent-project/\n    project.json\n    status.md\n    tasks/\n    next-actions/\n    decisions/\n    context/\n    operations/\n    artifacts/\n    runs/\n    handoffs/\n    reviews/\n    .generated/\n```\n\n---\n\n# 20. 我建议拍板的核心设计\n\n我建议 project 结构定成：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/project.json 是单项目事实来源\nproject-manager/registry.json 是全局查询索引\nstatus.md 是人类可读摘要\ntasks/ next-actions/ decisions/ 分文件存储\noperations/ 专门支持持续项目\nrelations 支持项目/skill/workflow/repo 关联\nlabels/tags 支持灵活查询\n```\n\n核心 `project.json` 采用：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"apiVersion\": \"agent-project/v1\",\n  \"kind\": \"Project\",\n  \"metadata\": {},\n  \"spec\": {},\n  \"status\": {},\n  \"current\": {},\n  \"operations\": {},\n  \"relations\": {},\n  \"timestamps\": {}\n}\n```\n\n核心查询字段压平到 registry：\n\n```text\nid\nname\naliases\nroot\nproject_type\nproject_mode\nowner\ndomain\ntags\nlabels\nlifecycle\nphase\nactivity\nhealth\ndelivery\nattention\ncurrent_task_id\ncurrent_next_action_id\nlast_activity_at\nupdated_at\nis_stale\nis_missing\n```\n\n这样查询会很舒服：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager query --mode ongoing --phase operations --health yellow\nmycli project-manager query --type capability --delivery published\nmycli project-manager query --attention needs_user_decision\nmycli project-manager query --name 素材库\n```\n\n这套结构既兼容旧的 `todo/done/sustained` 思路，也能支持持续性项目和未来复杂查询。","time":{"start":1777014329785,"end":1777014446004}}}
